    number comp_exp_ratio - sets the ratio of the compressor/expander; 0.1(1:10.0)-100(100:1.0); 1(1.0:1) is default
    number n - unknown
    number o - unknown
    number fade2 - negative with fade_in set; positive with fadeout-set
