function ultraschall.GetMediafileAttributes(filename)
--[[
<US_DocBloc version="1.0" spok_lang="en" prog_lang="*">
  <slug>GetMediafileAttributes</slug>
  <requires>
    Ultraschall=4.00
    Reaper=5.40
